	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Hail all !<BR>
<BR>
Drop:<BR>
<BR>
Fine Steel Weaponry, Amber, Jade, Pearl, Topaz, Words, Runes, Gloves of Rallos Zek, Flame of Vox, Ice Giant Toes, Silver Amulet, Ivory and Essence of Winter. Cash drop range from only Silver and Copper to as much as 50 Platinum.<BR>
<BR>
As a Shaman, dont try to solo these without having TURGURS, otherwise ye in for some pretty close battles. When ye able to, follow this routine:<BR>
<BR>
1. Summon Frenzied Spirit<BR>
2. Alacrity and Spirit of Wolf it<BR>
3. Harnessing of Spirit, Spirit of Wolf, Alacrity,    <BR>
   Chloroplast yeself. Have Superior Heal meditated<BR>
4. Cannibalize 1 yeself back up til ye have at least 80% of Mana.<BR>
5. Ye Spell Line-up should now read as follows:<BR>
<BR>
Superior Heal<BR>
Cannibalize 1<BR>
Alacrity<BR>
Chloroplast<BR>
Tugur&#180;s Insects<BR>
Incapacitate<BR>
Plague<BR>
Envenomed Bolt<BR>
<BR>
6. Start with sending pet on Giant, try to keep a distance. Let it whack on pet 4 to 5 times, then TUGURS. When ye lucky, pet can taunt it off you before it reaches ye, giving ye the chance to send in PLAGUE without being interrupted. After that it will be mainly on you. Cast INCAPACITATE right after Plague, and then ENVENOMED BOLT. Now battle it down with ye pet, ye might want to apply a Heal if needed.<BR>
<BR>
Tip: When battling the front spawns, send in pet while running to the outside, keeping the wall between you and the Ice Giant. Gives ye the chance to Slow, DOT and Debuff until he reaches ye, since he trys to walk directly through the wall, which takes a bit...<BR>
<BR>
Kubax Gurtholfin, the &quot;Spear of Justice&quot;<BR>
Proud Mystic of The Tribunal, 54th Winter<BR>
Order of Mjolnir<BR>
Tunare Server
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
